<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 16:08:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“他们是来杀人的”：以色列定居者袭击巴勒斯坦村庄后，当地人担心没有人来拯救他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village-locals-fear-theres-no-one-to-save-them/00000191-65d2-d3bf-a3b1-edf7aaa40000</link><description>周四，以色列定居者在约旦河西岸吉特村杀害了一名 23 岁男子，当地居民表示，这次袭击是一次精心策划的袭击，他们担心还会再次发生</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 15:27:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village-locals-fear-theres-no-one-to-save-them/00000191-65d2-d3bf-a3b1-edf7aaa40000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列在高级官员被杀之前破坏了真主党的通信网络</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/report-israel-breached-hezbollahs-communications-network-before-top-officials-killing/00000191-65f3-dda8-af9b-65f3cde50000</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，福阿德·舒克 (Fuad Shukr) 在以色列袭击导致他死亡之前接到电话，告诉他该去哪里</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 15:09:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/report-israel-breached-hezbollahs-communications-network-before-top-officials-killing/00000191-65f3-dda8-af9b-65f3cde50000</guid></item><item><title>《时代》杂志对内塔尼亚胡的采访进行了事实核查——他所说的并非全部都是真的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/time-fact-checked-their-interview-with-netanyahu-not-everything-he-said-was-true/00000191-654a-d772-a9d5-6ffe12090000</link><description>此次接受《时代周刊》采访是首相自10月7日以来第27次接受外国媒体采访，在接受该杂志工作人员核实后，他在采访中发表了一些虚假言论。</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 13:15:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/time-fact-checked-their-interview-with-netanyahu-not-everything-he-said-was-true/00000191-654a-d772-a9d5-6ffe12090000</guid></item><item><title>国防部消息人士称，警方拒绝调查试图渗透巴勒斯坦村庄的以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/police-refused-to-probe-israeli-who-tried-to-infiltrate-palestinian-village-source-says/00000191-6450-d478-a99b-f77580fc0000</link><description>六名以色列人试图进入纳布卢斯以南的一个巴勒斯坦村庄，其中一些人戴着面具，但在以色列军队到达现场后逃离。此前，定居者上周袭击了约旦河西岸的一个巴勒斯坦村庄，造成一人死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 09:38:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/police-refused-to-probe-israeli-who-tried-to-infiltrate-palestinian-village-source-says/00000191-6450-d478-a99b-f77580fc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列窃听定居者、犹太学院学生和清真寺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-artist-eavesdropping-on-settlers-yeshiva-students-and-mosques/00000191-5c63-dd29-a7f3-7d6bdb240000</link><description>此外，一家传奇的特拉维夫书店从拉宾广场地区搬到了弗洛伦丁，而耶路撒冷的木偶戏剧节也将试图缓解战争的影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 07:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-artist-eavesdropping-on-settlers-yeshiva-students-and-mosques/00000191-5c63-dd29-a7f3-7d6bdb240000</guid></item><item><title>现在是拜登的表演：他能引导以色列和哈马斯达成加沙协议吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/biden-is-trying-to-talk-a-deal-into-existence-but-a-breakthrough-isnt-yet-on-the-horizon/00000191-61ab-d993-a5d7-ebef1ef70000</link><description>美国总统正试图营造积极情绪，希望实现加沙停火并挫败伊朗袭击，但相关人士却不那么乐观 ■ 即使没有全面战争，以色列北部居民的生活也是难以忍受的与真主党合作 ■ 右翼对约旦河西岸致命定居者骚乱的谴责远没有令人信服</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 03:01:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/biden-is-trying-to-talk-a-deal-into-existence-but-a-breakthrough-isnt-yet-on-the-horizon/00000191-61ab-d993-a5d7-ebef1ef70000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯前往中东，内塔尼亚胡表示以色列不能在停火谈判的一些关键问题上妥协</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-live/two-hamas-members-killed-in-idf-airstrike-in-west-bank-israel-attacks-targets-in-lebanon/00000191-635f-dd29-a7f3-675f3bac0000</link><description>以色列国防军在追捕在约旦河西岸重伤以色列保安人员的袭击者时，偷走了武器。 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在加沙被火箭弹重伤。 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：我们在某些事情上不能保持灵活性。军事和外交压力是释放人质的途径 ■ 内塔尼亚胡和布林肯将于周一在耶路撒冷总理办公室会面</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 02:57:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-live/two-hamas-members-killed-in-idf-airstrike-in-west-bank-israel-attacks-targets-in-lebanon/00000191-635f-dd29-a7f3-675f3bac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙南部发布更多撤离令，缩小人道主义区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-more-evacuation-orders-in-south-gaza-shrinking-safe-zone/00000191-61fe-dd29-a7f3-65ff11b10000</link><description>联合国表示，大多数加沙人已经流离失所，其中许多人被迫多次撤离，而且在整个战争期间，约 84% 的加沙地区已被疏散</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 21:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-more-evacuation-orders-in-south-gaza-shrinking-safe-zone/00000191-61fe-dd29-a7f3-65ff11b10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名两名在加沙战斗中丧生的预备役军人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-two-reservists-killed-in-gaza-fighting/00000191-61fa-d1d3-a5f7-71fe32c20000</link><description>约塔姆·伊扎克·佩莱德（Yotam Itzhak Peled）军官（后任）和莫迪凯·约瑟夫·本·肖姆（Mordechai Yosef Ben Shoam）少校（后任）均 34 岁，在加沙中部被爆炸装置炸死</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 21:26:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-two-reservists-killed-in-gaza-fighting/00000191-61fa-d1d3-a5f7-71fe32c20000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔让伊朗了解情况，以色列距离释放人质协议又近了一步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-cautiously-optimistic-after-hostage-release-talks-in-doha-netanyahu-says/00000191-61d8-d1d3-a5f7-71fe0eb50000</link><description>以色列消息人士澄清说，尽管多哈峰会在推进部分计划方面取得了“重大进展”，但仍在等待哈马斯的回应。正在努力安排周三在开罗举行的另一轮会谈</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 20:20:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-cautiously-optimistic-after-hostage-release-talks-in-doha-netanyahu-says/00000191-61d8-d1d3-a5f7-71fe0eb50000</guid></item><item><title>在谈判中持谨慎乐观态度的情况下，全国各地的以色列人呼吁达成释放人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/amid-cautious-optimism-in-talks-israelis-across-the-country-call-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-60d0-d017-abd9-f9f484c70000</link><description>“你得到了以色列人民的全力支持。人质的兄弟说：“不要羞于做出最道德、最犹太化的决定，把他们带回家。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 17:41:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/amid-cautious-optimism-in-talks-israelis-across-the-country-call-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-60d0-d017-abd9-f9f484c70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 316 天：加沙卫生官员称以色列国防军袭击导致加沙地带中部 17 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-316-gaza-health-officials-say-idf-strike-kills-17-in-central-strip/00000191-6146-d478-a99b-f77759c00000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人报告以色列对加沙中部的袭击造成 17 人死亡、数十人受伤 ■ 黎巴嫩卫生部：以色列袭击造成 10 人死亡；以色列国防军：袭击真主党武器储存设施 ■ 拜登官员：停火/人质协议谈判“现已进入最后阶段”。 ■ 以色列调查发现，以色列国防军士兵在周四的约旦河西岸定居者袭击中袖手旁观 ■ 以下是战争开始 316 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 17:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-316-gaza-health-officials-say-idf-strike-kills-17-in-central-strip/00000191-6146-d478-a99b-f77759c00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击造成十人死亡；真主党火箭弹袭击导致两名以色列国防军士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/ten-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-lebanon-hezbollah-rocket-barrage-wounds-two-idf-soldiers/00000191-6087-d1d3-a5f7-70ff66080000</link><description>以色列军队报告称，它袭击了黎巴嫩南部的真主党武器储存设施以及其他与恐怖活动有关的地点。当地卫生部门表示，受害者包括一名母亲和她的两个孩子</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/ten-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-lebanon-hezbollah-rocket-barrage-wounds-two-idf-soldiers/00000191-6087-d1d3-a5f7-70ff66080000</guid></item><item><title>卫生官员称，以色列对加沙中部的袭击造成至少17名巴勒斯坦人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-17/ty-article/at-least-17-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-central-gaza-health-officials-say/00000191-60af-dd29-a7f3-65efeb620000</link><description>据加沙卫生官员称，死者中有八名儿童和四名妇女。以色列军方表示正在调查有关此次袭击的报道</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 15:02:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-17/ty-article/at-least-17-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-central-gaza-health-officials-say/00000191-60af-dd29-a7f3-65efeb620000</guid></item><item><title>“脊髓灰质炎的最终疫苗是和平”：加沙首例脊髓灰质炎病例促使人们呼吁开展疫苗接种计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-17/ty-article/gazas-first-polio-case-prompts-calls-for-vaccination-program-cease-fire/00000191-609c-d1d3-a5f7-70fe39010000</link><description>联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯在代尔巴拉赫出现确诊病例后表示，以色列和哈马斯之间的战斗暂停对于为加沙人接种疫苗以预防这种高传染性疾病至关重要</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 14:46:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-17/ty-article/gazas-first-polio-case-prompts-calls-for-vaccination-program-cease-fire/00000191-609c-d1d3-a5f7-70fe39010000</guid></item><item><title>塔梅尔在纳布卢斯志愿担任护理人员。他在执行任务时被以色列导弹炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/tamer-was-a-volunteer-paramedic-he-was-killed-in-the-line-of-duty-by-an-israeli-missile/00000191-5e7a-d017-abd9-fffe803d0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦难民营的一名 21 岁志愿护理人员被以色列导弹炸死，尽管他身穿表明自己是医务人员的橙色背心。他在他姐姐计划举行婚礼的那天去世了。自加沙战争爆发以来，以色列国防军也加大了对约旦河西岸的空袭力度</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 04:24:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/tamer-was-a-volunteer-paramedic-he-was-killed-in-the-line-of-duty-by-an-israeli-missile/00000191-5e7a-d017-abd9-fffe803d0000</guid></item><item><title>即使政府腐败，这个组织也能拯救以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/even-when-the-government-is-corrupt-this-group-can-save-israel/00000191-5e5d-db59-a5d1-7f5dc75b0000</link><description>2011年，摩萨德首脑阻止了轰炸伊朗的决定，但到了2024年，国防领域已经没有人像梅厄·达甘那样能够阻止内塔尼亚胡了。有骨气的专业人士可以使以色列免遭全面战争、民主制度的破坏以及香蕉共和国的转型</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 03:55:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/even-when-the-government-is-corrupt-this-group-can-save-israel/00000191-5e5d-db59-a5d1-7f5dc75b0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们永远无法在极端分子的主场击败他们。中间派必须做完全相反的事情”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/well-never-defeat-extremists-in-their-home-court-centrists-must-do-the-exact-opposite/00000191-5e29-dd29-a7f3-7f696e770000</link><description>超过 30 名政治家、知识分子、学者和作家共同撰写了一本由 Yair Lapid 的高级政策顾问编辑的新书，解释了为什么中间主义是治疗极端主义的良药</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 03:23:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/well-never-defeat-extremists-in-their-home-court-centrists-must-do-the-exact-opposite/00000191-5e29-dd29-a7f3-7f696e770000</guid></item><item><title>两名哈马斯成员在以色列国防军对约旦河西岸的空袭中丧生；以色列袭击黎巴嫩目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-live/.premium/lebanese-reports-6-killed-3-wounded-in-israeli-attributed-strike-in-southern-lebanon/00000191-5e13-d180-a9fd-dffb39660000</link><description>巴勒斯坦报道：以色列对加沙中部难民营的袭击造成 17 人死亡 ■ 以色列空袭约旦河西岸杰宁的汽车，两名哈马斯成员丧生 ■ 卫生官员称，以色列对黎巴嫩南部的袭击造成 10 人死亡 ■ 以色列谈判小组对局势表示“谨慎乐观”内塔尼亚胡办公室称加沙人质协议 ■ 哈马斯高级官员：“最新一轮会谈没有就重大问题达成一致”</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 02:22:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-live/.premium/lebanese-reports-6-killed-3-wounded-in-israeli-attributed-strike-in-southern-lebanon/00000191-5e13-d180-a9fd-dffb39660000</guid></item><item><title>调查显示定居者袭击巴勒斯坦村庄时以色列国防军部队袖手旁观</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/investigation-shows-settler-raid-on-palestinian-village-took-place-in-front-of-idf-forces/00000191-5ce6-d7bf-a5b9-fcf66a940000</link><description>一名高级国防官员说，士兵们“没有采取任何行动来阻止大屠杀，他们只是站在旁边，看到了一切，却什么也没做。”被杀巴勒斯坦人的尸体已被带去尸检，但结果无法确定是谁射杀了他</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 22:18:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/investigation-shows-settler-raid-on-palestinian-village-took-place-in-front-of-idf-forces/00000191-5ce6-d7bf-a5b9-fcf66a940000</guid></item></channel></rss>